long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Game Description
Welcome to the land of Jelly where all things are yummy and gooey! Test your matching skills as you match three jellies in a row. Be quick and level up!

Note:- You can Play More Categories Game In This Extension.

Game Instructions
Tap or click the arrow to play.

Your goal is to clear as many lines of jellies as possible as quickly as you can! To do so, move 3 identical jellies to a row or diagonal. Tap the jelly and drag to the space you would like it to go. Jellies will fall and you can continue your mission to level up. Have fun!
